<view class="page">
  <view class="page-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">趋势不是审判</text>
    <text class="hero-title">决心仪表盘</text>
    <text class="subtext">这个仪表盘不会替你决定要不要离职。它只是帮你看见：哪些事情正在反复消耗你。</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{!hasRecords}}" class="empty-card trend-empty">
    <text>还没有足够记录生成趋势。</text>
    <text>先写下一条真实的日记就好。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-card status-card {{croissant.statusClass}}">
    <text class="section-title">Croissant 当前状态</text>
    <text class="status-name">{{croissant.status}}</text>
    <text class="status-wear">磨损值：{{croissant.wear}}</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{croissant.explanation}}</text>
    <text class="dashboard-protect">保护建议：{{croissant.advice}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="stats-grid">
    <view class="stat-card"><text class="num">{{stats.total}}</text><text>总记录数</text></view>
    <view class="stat-card"><text class="num">{{stats.negative}}</text><text>负面记录</text></view>
    <view class="stat-card"><text class="num">{{stats.positive}}</text><text>正面记录</text></view>
    <view class="stat-card"><text class="num">{{stats.highImpact30Days}}</text><text>近30天高影响事件</text></view>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-card">
    <text class="section-title">最常见的主要原因</text>
    <text class="reason">{{stats.topReason}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-card">
    <text class="section-title">主要原因分布</text>
    <view wx:for="{{reasonDistribution}}" wx:key="reason" class="reason-row">
      <view class="row between">
        <text>{{item.reason}}</text>
        <text>{{item.count}} 次</text>
      </view>
      <view class="bar-track">
        <view class="bar-fill" style="width: {{item.percent}}%;"></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-card advice-card">
    <text class="section-title">本周保护建议</text>
    <text class="advice">{{stats.advice}}</text>
  </view>

  <button class="sticker-button secondary" bindtap="goNewDiary">去写一条新日记</button>
  <button class="sticker-button green" bindtap="goExitTest">去做离职状态自测</button>
</view>
